WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.000
MkvDrama.net

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
♪That day♪

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
♪Nothing stays together forever♪

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
♪I've quit romance♪

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
♪Who hasn't failed again♪

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
♪Crying in death♪

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
♪And in life♪

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
♪Even now♪

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
♪We keep learning♪

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
♪It's no surprise♪

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
♪Being happy is so hard♪

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
♪Weirdly, I became a role model♪

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
♪On the day we met again, we said hi♪

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
♪It was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint♪

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
♪Who can do anything without regret♪

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
♪I am all right♪

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
♪May you live in peace♪

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
♪Let the world roar♪

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
♪Sounds like a carnival♪

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
♪Being alive is never dull♪

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
♪How wonderful to be free♪

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
♪I became even better without you♪

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
♪Nothing can be perfect♪

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
♪We bless each other in pain♪

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
♪We nod and smile♪

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
♪May we both be well♪

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.930
=Episode 16=

01:49.578 --> 01:50.218
Yan.

01:53.322 --> 01:54.442
I liked you

01:56.003 --> 01:57.162
and trusted you so much.

02:01.808 --> 02:03.760
How could you have been lying
to us for so long?

02:04.923 --> 02:05.802
I'm sorry, Mom.

02:09.523 --> 02:11.042
I'll take all the consequences.

02:14.843 --> 02:16.442
If this gets out,

02:16.442 --> 02:17.683
it'll affect Haoming

02:17.683 --> 02:19.042
and the company's reputation.

02:20.162 --> 02:21.403
You can't handle the result.

02:22.642 --> 02:24.243
I'll comply with your wishes.

02:24.882 --> 02:26.642
I won't make any excuses.

02:29.442 --> 02:30.322
I'm sorry, Dad.

02:31.202 --> 02:33.003
I know apologies aren't enough

02:33.283 --> 02:34.882
to make up for my mistakes.

02:35.803 --> 02:37.602
I'll bear all legal responsibilities.

02:38.922 --> 02:39.602
Now,

02:41.602 --> 02:43.442
the New District project
is just starting.

02:43.683 --> 02:44.843
It's the most critical phase.

02:45.283 --> 02:46.123
As for how you two

02:46.243 --> 02:47.642
handle personal matters,

02:47.882 --> 02:48.922
I won't interfere.

02:49.123 --> 02:50.482
But you must understand this:

02:51.963 --> 02:53.162
it absolutely cannot affect

02:53.162 --> 02:55.003
the company's prestige and reputation.

02:55.283 --> 02:55.922
I understand.

02:57.803 --> 03:00.482
Until the paperwork is finalized,

03:00.722 --> 03:02.523
I'll publicly claim
I'm starting a business.

03:11.722 --> 03:12.283
Mom, Dad,

03:14.442 --> 03:16.283
if Haochen returns and asks about me,

03:17.803 --> 03:19.922
just say I'm too busy to come back.

03:25.523 --> 03:26.243
I'm sorry.

03:38.803 --> 03:39.442
I'm sorry.

03:46.106 --> 03:51.480
♪No one notices me
quietly exiting the stage♪

03:53.648 --> 03:55.248
♪When I return♪

03:55.344 --> 03:59.688
♪To the corner where I sheltered
from rain and tears♪

04:00.208 --> 04:07.146
♪Only then did I realize
what I had was precious♪

04:07.280 --> 04:12.042
♪Misplaced glory is just danger's omen♪

04:12.042 --> 04:14.403
(Remember, 10 AM on the 8th
at the Civil Affairs Bureau.)

04:15.056 --> 04:18.671
♪When city lights light,
but there's nowhere to turn to♪

04:19.084 --> 04:22.396
♪How should I compromise?♪

04:22.736 --> 04:26.486
♪When life resumes and settles the past♪

04:26.512 --> 04:30.499
♪No need to hide this flustered state♪

04:30.499 --> 04:34.273
♪Let my candor redeem my recklessness♪

04:34.274 --> 04:38.576
♪Forgive myself♪

04:38.576 --> 04:40.336
♪What kind of me♪

04:40.618 --> 04:43.248
♪Is the best me?♪

04:48.082 --> 04:48.762
Nice shot.

04:49.603 --> 04:51.003
I haven't played in ages.

04:51.603 --> 04:54.243
What brings you out today, Haoming?

04:55.202 --> 04:57.563
I mainly wanted to update you on work.

04:58.882 --> 04:59.923
Don't mention that.

05:00.563 --> 05:01.642
Our New District project

05:01.642 --> 05:02.723
is progressing smoothly.

05:03.003 --> 05:05.282
The planning permit
has been officially approved.

05:06.163 --> 05:07.163
With you overseeing it,

05:07.282 --> 05:08.762
I have no worries at all.

05:10.762 --> 05:11.322
Haoming,

05:13.123 --> 05:14.202
there's a personal matter

05:14.563 --> 05:16.003
that I'm hesitant to ask about.

05:17.282 --> 05:17.842
Go ahead.

05:18.522 --> 05:19.243
Lately,

05:19.483 --> 05:20.923
I've heard some rumors

05:21.363 --> 05:23.202
about your wife, Xu Yan, resigning.

05:24.043 --> 05:25.043
What's going on?

05:26.363 --> 05:27.683
She's starting her own business.

05:31.603 --> 05:33.483
There are things you might not know.

05:34.043 --> 05:35.123
Even now,

05:35.402 --> 05:37.522
Xu Yan regularly
visits my mother-in-law.

05:38.123 --> 05:39.762
Every time my mother-in-law sees her,

05:39.762 --> 05:41.603
she's overjoyed.

05:42.642 --> 05:43.803
I always thought

05:44.003 --> 05:45.923
once we established cooperation,

05:46.762 --> 05:49.123
she'd stop putting effort into her.

05:50.762 --> 05:54.282
I didn't expect
she'd be truly remarkable.

05:56.202 --> 05:58.123
You two are well-matched.

05:58.683 --> 06:00.842
I can see that as family,

06:01.163 --> 06:02.563
she genuinely cares for you.

06:04.723 --> 06:05.723
Thank you.

06:06.483 --> 06:08.243
Forgive my bluntness.

06:28.762 --> 06:30.243
(You're a typical boss.)

06:30.683 --> 06:32.003
Your expression of emotions

06:32.003 --> 06:33.040
has become transactional.

06:33.842 --> 06:34.962
I just want to give you

06:35.642 --> 06:36.842
the life you want.

06:37.402 --> 06:38.923
You are all I want.

06:40.522 --> 06:42.723
Convincing them wasn't easy.

06:43.243 --> 06:45.363
Luckily, I have a capable wife.

06:45.842 --> 06:47.202
This deal couldn't have been done

06:47.603 --> 06:48.522
without you.

06:49.723 --> 06:50.402
Are you okay?

07:09.522 --> 07:11.842
Hello?

07:12.163 --> 07:12.522
Hello.

07:12.522 --> 07:14.202
I called earlier.

07:14.202 --> 07:15.202
It's over half an hour.

07:15.202 --> 07:16.642
When will you come to fix the pipe?

07:17.363 --> 07:18.762
Soon. I've sent someone.

07:19.762 --> 07:21.363
Give me a specific time.

07:23.043 --> 07:23.803
I'll hurry.

07:42.803 --> 07:43.642
So fast?

07:45.402 --> 07:47.282
Coming. Please...

07:52.043 --> 07:53.363
Wh-Why are you here?

07:54.402 --> 07:54.962
I...

07:56.762 --> 07:57.723
What are you...

08:00.442 --> 08:02.803
Maybe we should wait for maintenance.

08:03.723 --> 08:04.603
Take a break.

08:04.842 --> 08:06.442
Done. Try it now.

08:07.003 --> 08:07.762
Turn on the tap.

08:08.762 --> 08:09.282
Well?

08:09.882 --> 08:11.123
Turn it off! Turn it off now!

08:12.163 --> 08:13.363
Hand me that tape.

08:14.003 --> 08:15.043
T-Tape?

08:15.123 --> 08:16.282
Use paper towels to wipe it.

08:17.243 --> 08:17.842
How much?

08:18.282 --> 08:19.202
It's okay. I can do it.

08:19.603 --> 08:20.043
Okay.

08:20.163 --> 08:20.962
Thanks.

08:21.003 --> 08:21.642
No problem.

08:23.723 --> 08:24.163
Done.

08:24.962 --> 08:25.683
Are you sure?

08:26.322 --> 08:27.003
Step back a bit.

08:27.003 --> 08:28.522
I'm turning the water on. Be careful.

08:34.162 --> 08:34.843
Fixed, right?

08:35.922 --> 08:37.003
Thank you.

08:37.282 --> 08:38.243
Thank you.

08:39.042 --> 08:39.843
It was nothing.

08:40.802 --> 08:41.882
You should go wash up now.

08:41.922 --> 08:42.603
Just go.

08:42.603 --> 08:43.723
I already washed down there.

08:44.323 --> 08:45.282
Then dry yourself off.

08:45.282 --> 08:45.642
Okay.

08:45.682 --> 08:46.603
I made you some tea.

08:46.642 --> 08:48.522
Come out and drink some warm tea first.

08:50.282 --> 08:51.203
Have a seat.

08:54.083 --> 08:55.723
Here. Drink some tea.

08:55.882 --> 08:56.443
Thank you.

09:00.723 --> 09:01.123
Here.

09:03.723 --> 09:04.243
Thanks.

09:05.003 --> 09:05.723
Don't mention it.

09:06.682 --> 09:08.682
You moved out without telling anyone.

09:08.963 --> 09:10.963
I asked your assistant to find out.

09:11.843 --> 09:13.042
You have your sister,

09:13.616 --> 09:15.344
and me, your fellow townsman
and classmate.

09:15.562 --> 09:17.042
You can share your troubles with us.

09:17.723 --> 09:19.083
We can help you find solutions.

09:20.162 --> 09:21.762
Be it work or personal issues.

09:22.522 --> 09:23.922
They are all minor issues.

09:23.963 --> 09:24.922
I can handle them.

09:26.123 --> 09:28.042
Besides, everyone has
their own life path.

09:28.042 --> 09:29.162
I can't trouble you guys

09:29.162 --> 09:30.203
with every little thing.

09:32.123 --> 09:33.443
You're always so formal with me.

09:38.203 --> 09:39.243
How's the job hunt going?

09:39.522 --> 09:40.123
Any progress?

09:40.843 --> 09:42.123
I haven't started looking yet.

09:44.162 --> 09:44.723
Right.

09:45.483 --> 09:46.922
Jobs are scarce these days.

09:47.762 --> 09:48.922
But don't stress about it.

09:49.603 --> 09:52.603
Take this time to relax
and get organized.

10:00.003 --> 10:01.762
When we have time, your sister and I

10:02.762 --> 10:04.243
will cook you some home-style dishes.

10:05.762 --> 10:08.243
Eating instant noodles
and frozen dumplings every day

10:09.083 --> 10:09.762
isn't healthy.

10:11.603 --> 10:15.083
You've been busy in the hospital,

10:15.323 --> 10:16.882
and you need to take care of Qiao Lin.

10:18.402 --> 10:20.003
Don't worry about me. I'm fine.

10:20.083 --> 10:22.042
I can handle anything. Really.

10:24.802 --> 10:25.402
Xu Yan,

10:27.642 --> 10:30.843
actually, I came today
because I wanted to...

10:30.843 --> 10:31.402
Yiming,

10:34.963 --> 10:36.843
I know you used to like me.

10:37.083 --> 10:38.802
But in my heart, I've always seen you

10:38.802 --> 10:40.682
as a fellow townsman and classmate.

10:41.243 --> 10:42.483
Nothing more. Okay?

10:42.723 --> 10:43.762
You're misunderstanding.

10:46.083 --> 10:46.483
Yes.

10:47.203 --> 10:48.323
I had feelings for you.

10:48.963 --> 10:50.123
And I confessed to you.

10:50.922 --> 10:52.323
It's my most innocent

10:52.323 --> 10:53.642
and beautiful memory from 18.

10:54.003 --> 10:55.282
Besides, it's been so long now.

10:56.243 --> 10:57.083
I've moved on.

10:58.323 --> 11:00.042
No matter what happens,

11:00.402 --> 11:01.123
if you're in need,

11:01.802 --> 11:02.522
I'll help you,

11:02.522 --> 11:03.282
no reason needed.

11:03.802 --> 11:06.083
Just like today, I'm just here
to check on you.

11:06.843 --> 11:08.042
So don't feel burdened.

11:08.882 --> 11:09.882
If you need anything,

11:10.402 --> 11:12.042
just tell me or your sister.

11:12.083 --> 11:12.922
It's the same.

11:14.603 --> 11:15.963
After all, your sister and I...

11:21.083 --> 11:22.203
Qiao Lin...

11:24.922 --> 11:27.323
Qiao Lin is actually wonderful.

11:31.402 --> 11:32.363
Behave well.

11:34.003 --> 11:35.963
I'll dry my clothes and leave now.

11:36.443 --> 11:37.042
Well,

11:37.042 --> 11:38.363
the hairdryer's in the bathroom.

12:04.243 --> 12:04.723
What...

12:06.123 --> 12:06.963
What brings you here?

12:08.843 --> 12:10.123
Divorce Supplementary Agreement.

12:10.562 --> 12:11.243
(Divorce Supplementary Agreement)
Here you are.

12:14.723 --> 12:15.443
Got it.

12:17.203 --> 12:18.723
I'll have it delivered after signing.

12:26.162 --> 12:27.282
Since I'm free today,

12:28.203 --> 12:29.802
let's go through each clause.

12:37.723 --> 12:38.922
- You have a visitor?
- Yes.

12:40.802 --> 12:41.402
May I start?

12:43.922 --> 12:44.922
Sure.

12:48.162 --> 12:49.162
Let's review each clause.

12:49.522 --> 12:50.642
Any additions you want?

12:51.682 --> 12:52.363
No rush.

12:53.123 --> 12:53.802
Take the time.

13:02.443 --> 13:03.562
Xu Yan, I'm done drying.

13:10.003 --> 13:10.882
And this is?

13:11.963 --> 13:13.723
My high school classmate, Yu Yiming.

13:19.762 --> 13:20.483
Shen Haoming.

13:22.203 --> 13:23.243
So he's your...

13:23.603 --> 13:24.162
Husband.

13:25.642 --> 13:26.162
Hello.

13:27.203 --> 13:27.723
Hello.

13:28.802 --> 13:29.922
I'll leave you two alone.

13:30.003 --> 13:31.402
I'll head back now.

13:31.802 --> 13:32.922
- I'll walk you out.
- No need.

13:34.282 --> 13:34.843
Thanks.

13:35.083 --> 13:35.642
My pleasure.

13:35.723 --> 13:36.162
Take care.

13:37.203 --> 13:38.203
Thanks, Yiming.

13:38.402 --> 13:38.882
Anytime.

13:44.682 --> 13:45.562
Shall we start?

13:46.922 --> 13:49.042
There's a clause
in the supplementary agreement:

13:49.723 --> 13:51.042
even if we do divorce,

13:51.443 --> 13:52.723
you need my approval

13:53.162 --> 13:54.762
before making any public announcements.

13:55.922 --> 13:57.402
Considering my company's reputation,

13:57.642 --> 13:59.562
mind your words and actions.

14:02.443 --> 14:04.123
Have I been inappropriate?

14:04.802 --> 14:05.363
No.

14:06.162 --> 14:07.483
I know Yu Yiming

14:07.682 --> 14:09.003
is your sister's boyfriend.

14:15.882 --> 14:17.323
You shouldn't be in business.

14:18.443 --> 14:20.003
You should be a spy.

14:21.123 --> 14:22.562
Just friendly advice.

14:23.363 --> 14:24.363
Let me remind you too:

14:25.642 --> 14:28.882
Tomorrow's the 8th.
See you at the Civil Affairs Bureau.

14:29.042 --> 14:29.562
Fine.

14:31.762 --> 14:32.723
And I'll remind you:

14:33.882 --> 14:34.723
Sign this.

14:35.690 --> 14:38.352
(Divorce Registration
Acceptance Receipt)

14:40.762 --> 14:42.083
Divorce cooling-off period?

14:42.243 --> 14:43.162
(Marriage Registration Office)
You don't know?

14:43.243 --> 14:44.162
Agreement divorces now

14:44.162 --> 14:45.402
have a cooling-off period.

14:45.603 --> 14:46.562
As the name suggests,

14:46.562 --> 14:47.603
it gives couples time

14:47.642 --> 14:50.003
to reconsider it
and avoid rash decisions.

14:50.483 --> 14:51.723
Your divorce application

14:51.723 --> 14:52.762
will be processed first.

14:53.042 --> 14:54.562
Your cooling-off period lasts a month.

14:54.723 --> 14:55.402
During this time,

14:55.522 --> 14:57.042
if you cancel the divorce,

14:57.483 --> 14:58.483
don't come back.

14:58.522 --> 14:59.922
The application will be revoked.

15:00.083 --> 15:01.882
If you still can't reconcile,

15:01.922 --> 15:02.723
return then.

15:03.642 --> 15:04.323
Next couple.

15:23.603 --> 15:24.282
I'm done.

15:24.483 --> 15:25.522
This tastes awful.

15:27.083 --> 15:28.723
What's wrong? Why the sudden temper?

15:29.323 --> 15:32.162
Aren't these all your usual favorites?

15:32.443 --> 15:34.483
I want my sis-in-law's
Longjing Tea Shrimp.

15:37.363 --> 15:38.448
She's starting a business

15:38.642 --> 15:39.802
and works long hours daily.

15:40.243 --> 15:41.483
She can't cook for you.

15:42.483 --> 15:44.522
Can't she live here
while building her business?

15:45.203 --> 15:46.682
You must have upset her

15:46.682 --> 15:47.562
and won't admit it.

15:47.642 --> 15:48.443
Haochen.

15:51.443 --> 15:52.963
Mind your tone with your brother.

16:03.243 --> 16:04.363
What's wrong now?

16:05.843 --> 16:06.642
Have more fish.

16:06.922 --> 16:08.762
You love steamed fish, don't you?

16:10.323 --> 16:11.323
My fault.

16:11.483 --> 16:13.483
Ms. Yu prefers Yan's steamed fish.

16:13.603 --> 16:15.443
I never get the technique right.

16:15.562 --> 16:16.642
The flavor's not the same.

16:17.483 --> 16:18.483
It's fine. It's good.

17:34.442 --> 17:39.120
(Sunshine, Coolest Rider, Horseback Day)

17:47.003 --> 17:48.203
(People say)

17:49.842 --> 17:53.443
a happy childhood
can heal you for a lifetime.

17:55.883 --> 17:57.042
But an unhappy one

18:00.322 --> 18:01.683
takes a lifetime to heal.

18:06.963 --> 18:08.042
That's why I believe

18:09.122 --> 18:10.963
no material comforts

18:12.322 --> 18:14.723
can replace family love and presence.

18:16.643 --> 18:17.963
Haochen's too young.

18:20.122 --> 18:22.883
Can't we ask your parents to reconsider?

18:32.243 --> 18:32.963
(Xu Yan's Resume)
Gezi,

18:34.362 --> 18:36.362
I'm willing to reduce my salary by 20%,

18:36.432 --> 18:38.128
the probation period
can be negotiated too,

18:38.322 --> 18:40.368
and I'll follow your scheduling
for show timeslots.

18:40.883 --> 18:42.122
Just give me a chance,

18:42.362 --> 18:44.282
and I'll prove myself worthy.

18:44.762 --> 18:47.042
Xu, I'm truly sorry,

18:47.483 --> 18:49.322
but we don't have
suitable jobs for you now.

18:50.762 --> 18:51.802
You know that

18:51.883 --> 18:53.203
the positions are all occupied.

18:53.483 --> 18:55.203
Unless someone quits,
takes medical leave,

18:55.203 --> 18:56.443
or has other emergencies,

18:56.483 --> 18:58.762
our lead hosts
could stay until retirement.

18:59.122 --> 19:01.602
Once you are out of the structure,

19:03.243 --> 19:04.762
it's hard to get another opportunity.

19:09.122 --> 19:09.923
Thank you.

19:21.643 --> 19:22.842
Where's Qu?

19:23.562 --> 19:24.282
Alright.

19:24.602 --> 19:25.403
Let's begin.

19:26.923 --> 19:29.522
Chapter 3, Article 6
of Jinda's Articles of Association

19:29.602 --> 19:30.762
regarding board election

19:31.203 --> 19:32.522
states that to ensure validity,

19:32.802 --> 19:34.322
over 90% of board members

19:34.362 --> 19:35.802
must attend.

19:36.003 --> 19:38.802
Those absent will be
considered abstentions.

19:39.203 --> 19:41.163
We have 13 present members

19:41.322 --> 19:42.243
and 1 absence,

19:42.322 --> 19:43.403
meeting the requirements.

19:43.643 --> 19:44.562
The election is valid.

19:45.362 --> 19:47.282
Now we'll vote on Shen Haoming's

19:47.282 --> 19:50.082
admission to the board.

19:50.762 --> 19:52.883
Those in favor of him,
please raise hands.

20:01.243 --> 20:01.842
Six votes.

20:03.562 --> 20:04.403
Those who oppose,

20:04.403 --> 20:05.602
please raise hands.

20:12.042 --> 20:12.522
Okay.

20:13.122 --> 20:14.923
With Qu's abstention,

20:15.082 --> 20:18.322
current votes are
six in favor and six against.

20:18.723 --> 20:19.403
Chairman,

20:20.003 --> 20:21.003
your vote is decisive.

20:32.443 --> 20:34.082
The chairman's family

20:34.362 --> 20:35.443
has been troubled lately.

20:36.243 --> 20:36.963
Oh?

20:37.443 --> 20:39.643
Shen Haoming's wife quit her job

20:40.403 --> 20:42.802
and moved out.

20:43.003 --> 20:45.643
Rumors say they're divorcing

20:45.802 --> 20:47.163
and dividing assets.

20:47.562 --> 20:50.082
I always knew
that guy's not an easy one.

20:50.362 --> 20:51.203
I heard

20:51.322 --> 20:53.562
he was wild in England,

20:54.243 --> 20:55.883
living a messy personal life

20:56.122 --> 20:58.003
surrounded by women.

20:59.042 --> 21:01.122
And he wants board membership?

21:02.163 --> 21:05.203
That board seat isn't meant for him.

21:06.602 --> 21:07.963
As you know,

21:08.362 --> 21:12.203
he's the heir backed by his father.

21:13.042 --> 21:14.243
What can we say?

21:14.522 --> 21:16.562
We built Jinda Group together

21:16.562 --> 21:17.762
for years.

21:18.243 --> 21:20.042
We can't let his father dictate all.

21:20.322 --> 21:21.443
(Anyway, at the meeting,)

21:21.562 --> 21:22.403
(I'll object.)

21:24.483 --> 21:25.163
I object.

21:26.443 --> 21:28.282
Seven against, six in favor.

21:31.562 --> 21:33.562
Shen Haoming fails to join the board.

21:34.842 --> 21:35.243
Alright.

21:35.362 --> 21:36.203
Meeting adjourned.

21:43.802 --> 21:45.362
I thought we had an agreement.

21:45.683 --> 21:47.163
I'd resolve the company crisis

21:47.522 --> 21:48.923
and develop new projects

21:49.403 --> 21:50.723
for a board seat.

21:52.082 --> 21:52.522
Yes,

21:54.163 --> 21:56.042
but I reconsidered.

21:57.003 --> 21:57.762
You're unfit.

21:58.403 --> 21:59.122
Reasons?

21:59.883 --> 22:01.282
I question your self-control,

22:01.362 --> 22:03.802
decision-making skills, and maturity.

22:04.963 --> 22:06.282
Are you bringing that up again?

22:06.923 --> 22:07.483
Have a seat.

22:10.122 --> 22:10.923
Sit down.

22:15.243 --> 22:15.762
Haoming,

22:16.403 --> 22:17.163
you need to know

22:17.923 --> 22:19.602
that since childhood,

22:19.643 --> 22:20.562
you've always been

22:20.562 --> 22:21.562
a good kid in my eyes

22:21.562 --> 22:22.883
who excelled in studies.

22:23.003 --> 22:24.842
That's why I gave you freedom

22:25.322 --> 22:26.362
and space.

22:26.362 --> 22:27.403
I had you study abroad.

22:29.082 --> 22:29.802
At nineteen,

22:30.522 --> 22:32.403
life was just beginning.

22:32.403 --> 22:33.643
Dating was fine.

22:33.683 --> 22:35.122
You were free to date girls.

22:35.282 --> 22:36.883
Why did you insist on keeping that baby?

22:37.203 --> 22:38.643
Did you even listen

22:38.723 --> 22:40.122
to your mom and my advice?

22:40.522 --> 22:41.322
Did you consider

22:41.403 --> 22:42.802
what future that child would have?

22:43.042 --> 22:45.163
Did you consider your own future?

22:45.403 --> 22:46.203
Did you consider

22:46.362 --> 22:48.122
it could stain your reputation?

22:48.122 --> 22:49.723
I never saw Haochen's birth as a stain.

22:49.723 --> 22:50.602
How is it not?

22:54.163 --> 22:56.602
We've been covering this up
for you all along.

22:56.923 --> 22:58.042
If your rivals find out,

22:58.322 --> 23:00.042
if your competitors learn about this,

23:00.322 --> 23:01.483
they'll exploit it

23:01.643 --> 23:03.723
and destroy you. Understand?

23:04.602 --> 23:05.963
If they see you

23:06.483 --> 23:08.322
as a reckless playboy,

23:08.362 --> 23:11.082
irresponsible and impulsive,

23:12.082 --> 23:13.282
who'd trust you?

23:13.562 --> 23:14.683
Would the board

23:15.122 --> 23:16.403
or the shareholders believe you?

23:16.643 --> 23:17.362
Never.

23:17.683 --> 23:18.602
As for your marriage,

23:19.203 --> 23:21.443
we let you make the decision

23:22.042 --> 23:23.802
and choose your own wife.

23:24.403 --> 23:25.562
But what did you do?

23:26.003 --> 23:27.762
You picked a fraud.

23:28.883 --> 23:30.483
Her background,

23:30.483 --> 23:31.923
education, life history,

23:31.923 --> 23:34.282
you knew everything about her,

23:34.643 --> 23:36.122
yet you hid the truth.

23:36.683 --> 23:37.883
You lied to us.

23:38.842 --> 23:40.723
I can't tolerate this.
Do you understand?

23:43.362 --> 23:44.802
Lying was my mistake.

23:46.602 --> 23:48.163
But between Xu Yan and me,

23:48.762 --> 23:50.322
our relationship was equal.

23:51.562 --> 23:53.003
I accepted everything about her.

23:53.003 --> 23:54.483
We wouldn't have divorced

23:54.483 --> 23:55.322
if she hadn't asked.

23:55.403 --> 23:57.562
She quit her news anchor career

23:57.762 --> 23:59.322
and caused quite a stir.

24:00.403 --> 24:01.443
No more excuses.

24:02.443 --> 24:03.403
Go to Cheng'an County.

24:03.842 --> 24:06.762
Handle the delayed project
at our branch there.

24:07.762 --> 24:08.963
Resolve it before you return.

24:16.762 --> 24:17.443
Mr. Shen,

24:18.602 --> 24:20.243
are you sure you don't want me with you?

24:22.122 --> 24:23.762
The email specified

24:24.602 --> 24:26.403
that only I will be transferred.

24:26.963 --> 24:29.282
Taking you violates company policy.

24:29.522 --> 24:31.602
But that branch is
in such a remote area.

24:32.082 --> 24:33.683
I worry about you going alone.

24:36.403 --> 24:37.443
You'll be more useful

24:37.842 --> 24:39.042
staying at the headquarters.

24:39.643 --> 24:40.883
If anything happens,

24:41.362 --> 24:42.403
keep me informed.

24:45.562 --> 24:46.122
I'm leaving.

24:46.122 --> 24:48.443
(Mailbox: Interview Rejected)

24:48.443 --> 24:50.163
If no positions open up...

24:52.003 --> 24:52.443
Alright.

24:53.443 --> 24:54.802
If new opportunities arise,

24:55.003 --> 24:56.842
please notify me.

24:58.403 --> 24:59.122
Okay, thanks.

25:11.114 --> 25:14.416
(Makeup Artist Liao's Call)

25:15.122 --> 25:15.963
Hello, Liao?

25:15.963 --> 25:16.643
Any news?

25:17.842 --> 25:18.643
Good news.

25:23.883 --> 25:26.082
What's wrong with you people?

25:27.122 --> 25:28.243
I told you to recruit hosts,

25:28.322 --> 25:29.282
but after all this time,

25:29.322 --> 25:30.883
you've found none.

25:31.522 --> 25:32.082
Mr. Qiu,

25:32.082 --> 25:33.243
you know our challenges here:

25:33.483 --> 25:35.163
other hosts complain about

25:35.163 --> 25:36.203
low profit sharing

25:36.243 --> 25:37.403
or our schedule demands...

25:37.403 --> 25:38.522
Alright, cut that.

25:38.842 --> 25:39.522
All nonsense.

25:40.403 --> 25:41.003
Mr. Qiu.

25:41.923 --> 25:43.122
This is Xu Yan.

25:43.522 --> 25:45.243
The hottest anchor

25:45.243 --> 25:46.483
I mentioned to you before.

25:47.203 --> 25:48.923
You've seen Family Feast, right?

25:49.243 --> 25:51.282
She even hosted financial news before.

25:57.842 --> 25:58.483
Glad to see you.

26:00.483 --> 26:01.562
Hello, Mr. Qiu.

26:02.762 --> 26:03.963
I'm terribly sorry

26:04.003 --> 26:05.802
for bringing you in
for the sudden audition.

26:05.883 --> 26:06.522
Not at all.

26:07.003 --> 26:08.282
Thank you for the opportunity.

26:08.483 --> 26:09.282
Thank you, Liao.

26:11.003 --> 26:11.802
You read the script?

26:12.163 --> 26:12.842
Yes.

26:13.883 --> 26:15.003
But, Mr. Qiu,

26:15.522 --> 26:17.282
I adjusted it

26:17.282 --> 26:18.403
based on my interpretation.

26:18.522 --> 26:19.522
Would that be acceptable?

26:19.723 --> 26:21.762
No need to check. It's excellent.

26:22.282 --> 26:23.483
Actually, every host

26:23.643 --> 26:25.042
needs their own distinctive style.

26:25.562 --> 26:26.762
Shall we do the audition now?

26:27.643 --> 26:28.282
No problem.

26:28.802 --> 26:30.322
Hello, audience.

26:30.683 --> 26:32.122
Welcome to the 618

26:32.362 --> 26:34.282
Comfort Home Textiles live stream.

26:35.802 --> 26:36.923
Comfort Home Textiles

26:37.163 --> 26:38.483
has earned worldwide fame

26:38.483 --> 26:39.963
for its experimental brand image

26:40.163 --> 26:41.802
and premium sleep quality,

26:42.203 --> 26:43.203
captivating consumers

26:43.203 --> 26:44.762
both domestically and internationally.

26:45.602 --> 26:46.883
To show our gratitude,

26:46.963 --> 26:49.003
we're offering exclusive deals

26:49.042 --> 26:50.243
on our premium products.

26:50.602 --> 26:53.203
This 100% cotton bedding set

26:53.203 --> 26:54.362
in front of me

26:54.723 --> 26:56.483
has a 50% off discount

26:56.602 --> 26:58.282
in today's live stream.

26:58.802 --> 27:01.003
Bring premium comfort
to your bedroom tonight.

27:01.362 --> 27:01.842
Stop.

27:05.602 --> 27:06.362
Ms. Xu,

27:06.683 --> 27:08.723
are you reporting news
or selling products?

27:09.203 --> 27:10.762
This won't work.

27:10.762 --> 27:12.163
To keep viewers engaged,

27:12.282 --> 27:13.643
you need vocal projection.

27:13.923 --> 27:15.643
You need explosive energy in your words

27:15.842 --> 27:17.362
and make the viewers feel urgent,

27:17.643 --> 27:18.762
like they'll miss out.

27:19.203 --> 27:20.963
Create that vibe that not buying now

27:20.963 --> 27:22.443
means losing a fortune.

27:22.443 --> 27:22.923
Got it?

27:24.762 --> 27:26.003
Got it, Mr. Qiu.

27:26.322 --> 27:27.602
But I believe

27:27.602 --> 27:29.522
my natural strength lies in

27:30.723 --> 27:32.203
a more composed hosting style.

27:32.562 --> 27:33.282
Like...

27:35.443 --> 27:37.562
Professor Wu's lecturing style

27:37.762 --> 27:40.243
or Dr. Chen's lab presentations.

27:40.602 --> 27:42.282
That hosting approach

27:42.562 --> 27:43.923
might suit me better.

27:44.602 --> 27:45.082
True,

27:45.403 --> 27:46.362
those examples you gave

27:46.362 --> 27:48.282
are established star hosts.

27:48.643 --> 27:50.003
You're still new to this.

27:50.802 --> 27:51.923
If you keep this up,

27:52.042 --> 27:55.243
we'll be lucky to get twenty viewers.

27:56.003 --> 27:56.923
I'm sorry.

27:58.203 --> 27:59.122
Alright, I know

27:59.122 --> 28:00.322
you used to be a news anchor.

28:00.762 --> 28:03.163
This is indeed new to you.

28:03.522 --> 28:04.203
Hard to adapt.

28:04.443 --> 28:04.923
Well...

28:09.483 --> 28:10.522
I'll teach you how.

28:13.883 --> 28:14.483
Start!

28:14.963 --> 28:16.122
Break the price floor.

28:23.883 --> 28:25.042
Break the price floor.

28:26.042 --> 28:27.042
There you go. Try harder.

28:27.163 --> 28:27.602
Again.

28:27.963 --> 28:29.282
Break the price floor!

28:30.723 --> 28:31.923
Break the price floor!

28:32.042 --> 28:33.163
Yes, here you go.

28:33.163 --> 28:33.883
Repeat after me.

28:34.042 --> 28:36.003
Don't talk like a news anchor!

28:37.243 --> 28:38.842
Don't talk like a news anchor!

28:39.082 --> 28:40.522
Open up a new world!

28:41.362 --> 28:42.762
Open up a new world!

28:43.163 --> 28:44.522
Yes! Maintain that energy.

28:44.643 --> 28:45.522
Follow your script.

28:45.562 --> 28:46.362
Come on.

28:46.923 --> 28:48.042
No 599.

28:48.522 --> 28:49.643
No 499.

28:49.883 --> 28:51.082
No 299!

28:55.842 --> 28:56.883
Sorry, I need a moment.

28:58.483 --> 28:59.282
Alright.

29:00.163 --> 29:00.762
Never mind.

29:00.762 --> 29:02.042
I can try again. I'm sorry.

29:02.562 --> 29:03.362
Well, listen.

29:03.723 --> 29:05.443
You better sit out
tonight's live stream.

29:06.362 --> 29:08.923
Go back and practice more

29:09.203 --> 29:10.883
what I taught you.

29:11.963 --> 29:12.923
- Well, you...
- Here!

29:13.163 --> 29:14.522
I'll cover tonight's live stream.

29:14.683 --> 29:16.403
- Okay.
- Okay! Mr. Qiu, go!

29:43.042 --> 29:45.003
Welcome, Mr. Shen.

29:46.243 --> 29:48.963
Thank you for picking me up.
Appreciate the effort.

29:49.042 --> 29:50.122
Our pleasure.

29:50.522 --> 29:51.042
Luggage!

29:52.203 --> 29:53.802
Mr. Shen, let me show you around.

29:53.802 --> 29:54.203
Come on.

29:57.226 --> 29:58.683
(General Manager's Office)

29:58.683 --> 29:59.243
Mr. Shen.

29:59.842 --> 30:00.963
This will be your office.

30:03.522 --> 30:04.842
Hongyun is the smallest branch

30:04.842 --> 30:05.802
under Jinda Group.

30:06.643 --> 30:07.963
Our resources here are limited.

30:08.163 --> 30:09.322
Bear the humble facilities.

30:09.683 --> 30:11.122
Mr. Shen, hope you don't mind.

30:13.643 --> 30:14.602
Normally,

30:14.842 --> 30:15.762
you'd stay in a hotel.

30:16.883 --> 30:18.723
But our budget can't cover that expense.

30:18.883 --> 30:20.443
Please stay here for now.

30:20.963 --> 30:21.883
It's a bit cramped,

30:22.163 --> 30:24.842
but only managers can enjoy this.

30:26.082 --> 30:28.243
But the restroom is in the yard.

30:31.082 --> 30:31.762
Mr. Zhang.

30:32.163 --> 30:33.322
Please send me

30:33.403 --> 30:34.683
all the related files.

30:38.403 --> 30:39.443
Don't you want to rest?

30:39.643 --> 30:40.562
Straight into work now?

30:42.562 --> 30:43.522
When is the earliest

30:43.522 --> 30:44.602
you can send them to me?

30:46.683 --> 30:48.243
They're all here. I've prepared them.

31:00.003 --> 31:02.282
We've already reported
the issues to headquarters.

31:02.443 --> 31:02.923
Mr. Shen.

31:03.163 --> 31:04.602
Let me brief you again.

31:04.842 --> 31:05.683
Here's the thing.

31:06.322 --> 31:07.322
Project delay

31:07.683 --> 31:09.762
is due to material
and labor cost increases.

31:10.282 --> 31:12.362
Mr. Wu from Anqiang Construction.

31:12.483 --> 31:13.122
I think

31:13.443 --> 31:14.704
he thought profits were slim,

31:14.704 --> 31:17.842
so secretly borrowed money
claiming it was for project funding.

31:17.842 --> 31:19.683
Then he took the money and fled.

31:20.203 --> 31:21.122
We called the police.

31:21.163 --> 31:22.322
But in a situation like this,

31:22.562 --> 31:25.602
even if we catch him,
might still not recover the money.

31:26.602 --> 31:28.282
What's your alternative plan?

31:28.842 --> 31:31.042
I've activated the emergency fund

31:31.122 --> 31:32.362
to maintain daily operations.

31:32.562 --> 31:35.562
And I've applied for budget adjustment.

31:36.403 --> 31:37.602
If construction halts,

31:37.602 --> 31:38.322
fails to deliver,

31:38.562 --> 31:40.203
it would cause greater losses for us.

31:43.282 --> 31:44.883
So Mr. Shen,

31:46.003 --> 31:48.203
when can we get this budget?

31:51.203 --> 31:53.723
Only after I verify this.

31:55.203 --> 31:56.203
You'd better hurry then.

31:56.483 --> 31:57.883
The emergency fund can't last long.

32:03.003 --> 32:03.963
The inspection reports,

32:05.562 --> 32:06.384
construction logs,

32:09.243 --> 32:10.683
and building blueprints

32:11.042 --> 32:12.562
are all mixed together?

32:13.163 --> 32:14.042
No categorization?

32:14.483 --> 32:16.403
We're broke, Mr. Shen.

32:16.602 --> 32:18.443
We can barely keep
the construction team.

32:18.562 --> 32:20.243
I can't even afford a secretary

32:20.243 --> 32:23.082
or an assistant for you.

32:24.082 --> 32:26.282
Just let me know

32:26.282 --> 32:27.443
if you need anything.

32:27.522 --> 32:29.243
I'm mostly onsite daily,

32:29.243 --> 32:31.762
but I'll help when possible.

32:34.003 --> 32:35.243
Thank you.

32:36.602 --> 32:37.122
Mr. Zhang.

32:37.643 --> 32:38.602
I think we should host

32:38.602 --> 32:40.003
a banquet tonight

32:40.322 --> 32:42.483
to properly welcome Mr. Shen.

32:42.923 --> 32:43.883
No need.

32:44.683 --> 32:45.643
Trying to curry favor?

32:46.322 --> 32:46.842
You?

32:46.923 --> 32:48.403
I...

32:48.883 --> 32:50.282
I'm not fit for that.

32:51.403 --> 32:53.322
Li, I've told you many times

32:53.443 --> 32:54.483
(Staff Cafeteria)
not to waste efforts.

32:56.723 --> 32:57.802
I've figured it out.

32:59.403 --> 33:01.483
Chairman Shen didn't even
let him into the board.

33:02.163 --> 33:03.362
He's his biological son!

33:03.602 --> 33:04.403
How ruthless!

33:05.203 --> 33:07.483
He came back from abroad,

33:07.483 --> 33:08.562
but kept getting sidelined.

33:09.522 --> 33:10.802
Vice President sounds fancy,

33:11.163 --> 33:12.762
but it's just an empty title.

33:12.923 --> 33:15.122
Think about it.
They transferred him here

33:15.322 --> 33:16.723
without funding or manpower.

33:17.362 --> 33:18.003
For what?

33:18.443 --> 33:19.522
Enjoying his life here?

33:20.282 --> 33:21.963
Obviously, he's been discarded,

33:22.403 --> 33:22.963
abandoned.

33:23.762 --> 33:24.923
What if he notices something?

33:24.923 --> 33:25.883
What if?

33:25.923 --> 33:26.923
Notice what?

33:32.362 --> 33:33.403
Look at him.

33:34.042 --> 33:35.762
Does he know
construction site intricacies?

33:36.082 --> 33:36.802
Even I don't know.

33:38.003 --> 33:42.322
Plus, even I couldn't stand
such facilities and office setup.

33:42.322 --> 33:43.282
How long can he hold on?

33:43.362 --> 33:44.643
He'll leave soon.

33:53.624 --> 33:56.197
♪I like it when it's just me and you♪

34:00.106 --> 34:02.042
♪I think by now you know it♪

34:02.042 --> 34:04.522
Our loyal fans purchase a lot of times.

34:04.522 --> 34:06.362
And this problem won't happen.

34:07.322 --> 34:09.323
Enough talk.

34:10.562 --> 34:11.843
Let me show you

34:11.843 --> 34:14.283
our upgraded after-sales service.

34:14.323 --> 34:15.202
Let me show you...

34:15.722 --> 34:16.483
Let me show you

34:16.483 --> 34:18.443
our upgraded after-sales service.

34:18.883 --> 34:20.682
7-day no-reason return policy!

34:20.763 --> 34:21.602
15 days...

34:27.568 --> 34:30.288
♪Right now just to be here with you♪

34:30.443 --> 34:31.682
Attach the link!

34:31.843 --> 34:33.003
(Adding grilles to Xinwan Residence Phase 1)
Sold out!

34:34.952 --> 34:35.664
♪I like you♪

34:36.642 --> 34:38.682
7-day no-reason return policy

34:38.682 --> 34:39.522
is all set!

34:39.522 --> 34:40.803
7-day no-reason return policy

34:40.803 --> 34:41.642
is all set!

34:41.682 --> 34:42.843
Follow us

34:42.843 --> 34:47.722
so that you can reach us easily.

34:47.963 --> 34:50.202
We won't fail your trust.

34:50.736 --> 34:52.532
♪Feeling so lost and feeling♪

34:52.718 --> 34:54.304
♪So much distractions♪

34:54.442 --> 34:55.427
♪Never imagined♪

34:55.427 --> 34:57.580
♪You'd stay by my side♪

34:59.363 --> 35:01.483
Hi everyone! I'm the host, Xu Yan.

35:01.522 --> 35:03.242
Today I'm recommending

35:03.403 --> 35:05.883
bedding from a national brand.

35:05.963 --> 35:07.242
Backstage, pass me...

35:07.323 --> 35:08.403
Pass me the bedding. Okay?

35:08.483 --> 35:09.323
Thanks.

35:09.443 --> 35:11.242
How many units do we have today?

35:11.323 --> 35:12.202
200, right?

35:12.202 --> 35:13.003
Only 200 available.

35:13.042 --> 35:15.522
Regular price is 1999.

35:15.682 --> 35:18.403
But today just 299!

35:18.443 --> 35:20.042
Backstage team, let's get ready.

35:20.162 --> 35:21.602
Three, two, one.

35:23.562 --> 35:24.963
Three, two, one.

35:25.082 --> 35:26.363
Attach the link!

35:28.722 --> 35:29.763
Three, two, one.

35:29.803 --> 35:30.803
Attach the link!

35:30.883 --> 35:33.042
Three two one, attach the link!

35:33.642 --> 35:34.642
For those who want it

35:34.642 --> 35:36.363
click the top-left button...

35:37.003 --> 35:37.483
Left...

35:40.202 --> 35:41.162
For those who want it

35:41.162 --> 35:42.122
click the...

35:42.642 --> 35:43.602
For those who want it

35:43.602 --> 35:45.202
click the top-left link.

35:45.202 --> 35:45.722
Okay?

35:45.883 --> 35:49.082
High-density woven jacquard fabric.

35:49.122 --> 35:51.042
In superior quality!

35:51.202 --> 35:52.122
Let me show you

35:52.242 --> 35:54.042
the excellent craftsmanship.

35:54.162 --> 35:55.323
If you like it,

35:55.323 --> 35:57.082
click the top-left link...

36:03.749 --> 36:06.188
♪Just hope you feel the same way too♪

36:07.363 --> 36:08.443
199.

36:09.443 --> 36:10.562
(1999.)

36:10.722 --> 36:12.323
